summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-eighth Avenue No. from E. Prospect to East Blain Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 13713, creating Local Improvement District No. 1249 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
